This section covers notes for Item classes.

- If an Item class is made, name it using your mod's name or ID and then suffix Items, rather than "ModItems" since it can conflict with other mods.
    For Example: "BasemodItems"
- This is good because it defines the mod's name, "Basemod" and suffixes "Items" to indicate that it is an Item registration class.

- If an item has its own class for special functionality,